 ## Usage

+### Fanning a message out
+
+`fanout(recipients, message)` delivers one message to every recipient and
+returns one delivery record per recipient, in the order they were given.
+Messages longer than 240 characters are trimmed and end with an ellipsis.
+
+### Probing the notifier
+
 Call `probeNotifier(done)` once at startup. It runs the notifier binary with
 `--version` and calls back with `'ok'` or `'missing'`.

