+# Limits
+
+| Limit | Value | Why |
+|-------|-------|-----|
+| Body length | 240 characters | The desktop notifier truncates past this. |
+| Recipients per fanout | unbounded | Delivery is synchronous and cheap. |
+
+A trimmed body always ends with a single ellipsis character, so a reader can
+tell a trimmed message from a short one.
